  "Extended periods spanning several hundred years": "",
  "Continuous periods of multiple consecutive decades": "",
  "Geological timescales covering millions of years": "",
  "Weather refers to the short-term state of the atmosphere at a specific place and time, including temperature, precipitation, humidity, and wind conditions over hours to days.": "",
  "Climate is defined as the average weather conditions in an area over a period of at least:": "",
  "1 year": "",
  "10 years": "",
  "100 years": "",
  "30 years": "",
  "Climate is the average of weather patterns over at least 30 years, as defined by the World Meteorological Organization, providing a statistical picture of typical conditions.": "",
