  "Data from weather stations around the world": "",
  "Indirect evidence of past climate conditions preserved in natural records like ice cores, tree rings, and ocean sediments": "",
  "Data collected by weather satellites": "",
  "Proxy data are natural archives that preserve indirect records of past climate conditions, allowing scientists to reconstruct temperatures, precipitation, and atmospheric composition for periods before instruments existed.": "",
